{"tid":718160,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[Linux] 點樣可以令一個folder入面嘅嘢淨係可以被某一個program/script access?","createTime":"2018-06-26T14:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T00:35:33.000Z","uid":34664,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c65df939246cdf56a29ac78f46c052409d9c1d20","tid":718160,"uid":34664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T14:43:09.000Z","msg":"有一個program/script<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">~/ABC/ABC.sh</code></pre><br />\n佢就有啲config<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">~/ABC/config/一堆嘢</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n點樣可以做到以下效果：<br />\n1. 我自己可以繼續唔使sudo去run呢段script<br />\n2. config folder淨係可以被ABC.sh access<br />\n3. 即使係我自己都access唔到, 當然root另計啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原因：<br />\nconfig入面有敏感資料<br />\n而佢所在嘅呢部機有VPN+DNS+BT server共存<br />\n想盡量確保呢堆file安全?"},{"pid":"6a2b1eb87f35eb0c562bef78d7063ff62c36cb78","tid":718160,"uid":180281,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T14:47:50.000Z","msg":"ZIP+Password? 再經Program落Password auto un-ZIP<br />\n<br />\n利申: 其實唔識 9up"},{"pid":"f4aafbb3a6b0f83f0e49f96a377b63ba97b6e692","tid":718160,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T14:59:24.000Z","msg":"搭單問下<br />\n用用下中咗毒， chromium首頁變咗唔知乜Q嘢導航<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係我全部package都係來自patcher install, 最大可能喺邊到中招？"},{"pid":"08342c38610d2a15e36a6d70da107f179788727d","tid":718160,"uid":31837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:04:52.000Z","msg":"鳩估，chown?"},{"pid":"bedb2cdfd61ed06f14a15bfdb2f598137c1b42f9","tid":718160,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:24:24.000Z","msg":"如果自己唔可以Access嘅嘢<br />\n係咪唔應該擺喺自己個Home folder"},{"pid":"a58dbbacdfce6e219e31dd9d25c506cfe93f8630","tid":718160,"uid":63156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:42:41.000Z","msg":"用setuid"},{"pid":"bd849fda51477eee804f3